ick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adb8639ca3ce45a1eeb968ff68eb7f8b512dd84","tid":838210,"uid":44541,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:18:14.000Z","msg":"似係桃太郎老豆有時空果實 但有限制 例如死 (好似手術果實咁) 佢臨死前用果實能力送個五個人去未來保佢地條命<br />\n<br />\n有新劇情好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2446c7812f343166ab6eac89f95790b09b7e355","tid":838210,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/222221_c69ec5dbd58a7fc16de427daed830640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F222221_c69ec5dbd58a7fc16de427daed830640.jpg&h=0cfc2650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路飛：你們的秘密還真多啊！趕緊說吧！<br />\n錦衛門：呃&hellip;&hellip;實在抱歉。但是這個真的很難讓人相信&hellip;&hellip;你們認識的勘九郎和雷藏，以及這裡的我們3個&hellip;&hellip;總共5人，實不相瞞&hellip;&hellip;我們其實是「過去的人」！<br />\n路：誒？<br />\n錦：我們其實是來自20年前的和之國 我們穿越了時間！<br />\n所有人：誒？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/222223_16777678467a53f1b340f117ce689ed9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F222223_16777678467a53f1b340f117ce689ed9.jpg&h=db36c021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/222226_0d5245aefdd437c57dffa653102cdd69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F222226_0d5245aefdd437c57dffa653102cdd69.jpg&h=7f0adf2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/222227_0a9c38dd429b2971b65d3afe08e1cd0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018